Content.summary: 'Watch Entourage' - a blog post by Darren Ferguson about Human Interest, Entertainment Culture written on 09 September 2006
Content.bodyText:
I'm not really into opinionated blog posts, but just for once.....

If you haven't seen Entourage, then I recommend you watch it. Here are a couple of clips of Ari -one of the main characters - at his best. (Not for the easily offended).
